6/Pile-of-Hunqs-1.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/Pile-of-Hunqs-1.jpg?resize=768,767&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/Pile-of-Hunqs-1.jpg?resize=700,699&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2100\" height=\"2100\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?w=2100&amp;quality=75 2100w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/665_1857.jpg?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/silver-crank-widelo.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/silver-crank-widelo.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/silver-crank-widelo.jpg?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/silver-crank-widelo.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/silver-crank-widelo.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/silver-crank-widelo.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/collections/silver-cranks\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell SILVER Cranks Return in Several Configurations</a> $280</h3>\n<p>Whether you want a set for your new Roadini or your old beausaged Bombadil, Rivendell has a set of SILVER cranks for you. These square taper cranks look like the offerings from yesteryear while offering a variety of gear assemblages for any bike.</p>\n<p>The SILVER crank is cold-forged from 7075 T6 aluminum; the best grade for crankarms. It‚Äôs more expensive, but imparts a grain to the metal in a way that casting and machining doesn‚Äôt. It‚Äôs compatible with JIS taper bottom brackets, which are most of them, and the chainline is about 47 with a 110mm Shimano BB, and 50mm with a 113. The Q-Factor with a 107mm BB is 154mm.</p>\n<p>As with everything Riv-related, there‚Äôs a lot more to be said about these beautiful cranks, so roll on over to <a href=\"https://www.rivbike.com/collections/silver-cranks\" target=\"_blank\">Rivendell</a> to check out the restocked SILVER cranks.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1385\" height=\"779\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/unnamed.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/unnamed.png?w=1385&amp;quality=75 1385w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/unnamed.png?resize=1024,576&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/unnamed.png?resize=768,432&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/unnamed.png?resize=1335,751&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/unnamed.png?resize=700,394&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://bikefriday.com/product/bike-friday-haul-a-day-elite-cargo-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Bike Friday Haul-a-Day Cargo Bike</a> $1,995</h3>\n<p>The lightest and most versatile long-tail Cargo Bike in the world. Starting at 34lbs it carries up to 440lbs, the Haul-a-Day is unlike anything Bike Friday has offered before. What makes this platform so genius is its low center of gravity, making dismounting or mounting with a load a cinch. The frame adjusts to fit people 4ft 9 in to 6ft 6 in. E-assist is an option and you can disassemble the whole bike to pack into a car trunk for travel. Handmade from raw tubing in Oregon USA.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Parks vertically on its rear end for small footprint storage.</li>\n<li>Fits on many transport racks: bus, car, and train.</li>\n<li>Clearance for 2.25‚Äù tires with fenders and up to 2.4‚Ä≥ tires under certain component combinations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://bikefriday.com/product/bike-friday-haul-a-day-elite-cargo-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Bike Friday</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_olive_00_v6_1200.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_olive_00_v6_1200.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_olive_00_v6_1200.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_olive_00_v6_1200.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_olive_00_v6_1200.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_olive_00_v6_1200.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_sand_00_v6_1200x.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/MEN_SS_TECH_TEE_sand_00_v6_1200x.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/