lity=75 1152w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://missionworkshop.com/products/mission-pro-mens-tech-tee?variant=40623794782317\" target=\"_blank\">Mission Workshop Pro Tech Tees Land in Time for Summer</a> $108</h3>\n<p>The Mission Pro Tech Tee is constructed with an Italian open-knit dimensional-mesh that exponentially increases surface area for breathability and rapid drying. Enhanced wicking is accomplished by two different yarns creating a differential that pulls moisture away from the body. Works perfectly as a base layer, a jersey alternative or simply as a high-performance tee.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Italian open-knit dimensional-mesh</li>\n<li>100% Double Knit Poly</li>\n<li>Extended coverage in the back</li>\n<li>Differential yarns for enhanced wicking</li>\n<li>Quick drying</li>\n<li>Available in 4 colors</li>\n<li>Black, White: 110 GSM</li>\n<li>Sand, Olive: 120 GSM</li>\n<li>Made in Italy</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://missionworkshop.com/products/mission-pro-mens-tech-tee?variant=40623794782317\" target=\"_blank\">Mission Workshop</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/8-1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/8-1.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/8-1.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/8-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/8-1.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/6.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/6.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/6.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/6.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/6.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/1.1.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/1.1.jpg?w=1200&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/1.1.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/1.1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/1.1.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://outershell.com/shop/magic-musette\" target=\"_blank\">Outer Shell Magic Musette</a> $45</h3>\n<p>Our multipurpose, multimodal, Magic Musette packs into its own pocket and fits a 14‚Äù laptop with room to spare. It features both a zippered and snap button closure so you can choose to use either one, depending on what you‚Äôre packing. Included is a tiny removable stabilizer cord that keeps it on your back while riding, but is also easy to put away when you don‚Äôt want it.</p>\n<p>Stow the musette in your jersey pocket for that post ride burrito or bring it around town for your day-to-day.</p>\n<p>Available in five colors and shipping today from <a href=\"https://outershell.com/shop/magic-musette\" target=\"_blank\">Outer Shell</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod.jpg?w=768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod.jpg?resize=700,1050&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-1.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-1.jpg?w=768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-1.jpg?resize=700,1050&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-2.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-2.jpg?w=768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-2.jpg?resize=700,1050&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-3.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-3.jpg?w=768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/hmgoepprod-3.jpg?resize=700,1050&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www2.hm.com/en_us/search-results.html?q=cycling\" target=\"_blank\">H&amp;M DryMove‚Ñ¢ Cycling Bibs and Jersey</a> $99/49.99</h3>\n<p>Following brands like Zara, H&amp;M has released two pieces of cycling kit for the summer ‚Äô23 season: a set of DryMove‚Ñ¢ cycling bibs, complete with chamois, side cargo pocket, and a DryMove‚Ñ¢ jersey with a cinch at the bottom.</p>\n<p>Cycling bib shorts in breathable DryMove‚Ñ¢ functional fabric to wick away moisture from skin and keep you comfortably dry while moving. Snug fit with four-way stretch for added comfort and freedom of movement. Elasticized suspenders, mesh panel at back for maximum ventilation, and a cycling pad at gusset. Open leg pockets for easy access, concealed silicone trim at hem to keep legs in place, and reflective details at back.</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, the Cycling Jersey is a loose-fit, lightweight, stretchy jersey made from breathable DryMove‚Ñ¢ functional mesh to wick away moisture from skin and keep you comfortably dry while moving. Two-part pocket at back with flap, concealed drawstring at hem with cord stoppers, and reflective details on sleeves and at back.</p>\n<p>See the full cycling drop at <a href=\"https://www2.hm.com/en_us/search-results.html?q=cycling\" target=\"_blank\">H&amp;M</a>.</p>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<hr />\n<p>¬†</p>\n<div><span>Ôªø</span><span>Ôªø</span></div>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yg0HjbfqvHE\" target=\"_blank\">Inside the Veneto Trail</a></h3>\n<p>Amongst all the off-road cycling events within the area, <a href=\"https://venetotrail.eu/\" target=\"_blank\">the Veneto Trail</a> definitly stands out. An absolute breathtaking route, which was very obviously setup by a very passionate cyclist for like-minded passionate cyclists. <a href=\"https://www.bombtrack.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Bombtrack</a> takes us along on its company outing on this stunning trip.</p>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<hr />\n<p>¬†</p>\n<h3>Radavision</h3>\n<p>Stuff we see on the ‚Äònet that causes pause‚Ä¶</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1250\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?resize=1024,640&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?resize=768,480&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?resize=1800,1125&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?resize=1335,834&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?resize=700,438&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/06/SF-Pride-Parade-2023-A.Danger.jpg?resize=1536,960&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Photo via <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/adangerpdx/\" target=\"_blank\">@adangerpdx<br />\n</a></em></p>\n<p>Amy caught a wonderful photo in celebration of Pride while in San Francisco! üè≥Ô∏è‚Äçüåà</p>\n<p><em>If